headline.print_headline: Djokovic to Meet Nadal in Rome Final, Serena Through
headline.main: Djokovic to Meet Nadal in Rome Final, Serena Through

lead_paragraph: The Italian Open will get its dream men's final on Sunday after Rafa Nadal's routine cuffing of Grigor Dimitrov set up an enticing match with Novak Djokovic that could be a barometer for the French Open.
